表面处理；修饰；完成安装

完成；终结；完善；对（材料、物品）进行最后加工；润饰；用尽（所剩之物）；给…最后一道工序；达到终点；使结束运行；使筋疲力尽；（赛跑、竞赛）得…名
完成；结束；终点；最后部分；表面处理；光泽；抛光；结尾；结局；（漆完抛光后的）成品表面；末道漆；饰面；终结；终结线

sogou-kaoyan.v: 吃/喝光; 用尽[出现0次)]

sogou-gaokao.n: 最后部分;  结尾[出现0次)]

sogou-zhongkao.v: 完成; 结束[出现232次)];吃/喝光; 用尽[出现4次)]

1.en: He took a trip to southern California , and there he found just the weather and scenery he needed to finish his movie.
1.cn: 他去加洲南部旅行，在那里他恰好发现了要完成他的电影所需的财富和外景。

2.en: On top of that, the producer and director didn't want me to work too hard so they let me finish up after filming a couple of shots.
2.cn: 还有，制片、导演等人不想我太辛苦，拍了几个镜头就说让我收工。

3.en: When you finish eating your Hollywood ice cream cone, you immediately put it out of your mind, but that lollipop isn't so easily forgotten.
3.cn: 只是好莱坞冰淇淋吃多了，吃完会马上忘在脑后，这支棒棒糖却不这么简单？

0.en: And why not? 'Cause I didn't finish it.
0.cn: 为什么？因为我还没完成。

1.en: Sir, I would like to finish our briefing.
1.cn: 先生，我想先完成我们的讨论。

2.en: Nice racing, Padawan. You're the first to finish.
2.cn: 干得漂亮，我的绝地学徒。你是第一个完成的。

3.en: You had time to finish your little art project, but you didn't have time to finish your chores?
3.cn: 你有时间完成你那个小艺术品，但是却没有时间做完家务吗？

4.en: We're waiting, sir. Waiting for what? Private Doss to finish praying for us, sir.
4.cn: 我们在等着，长官。等着啥？列兵多斯完成为我们的祈祷，长官。

5.en: Now, it's not just the meatballs, that's gonna finish the dish and make them look like lion heads.
5.cn: 为了完成这道菜，让它们看起来像狮子头，光有肉丸不够。

6.en: So you have to finish what you're doing and you have to come home to her. You have to come home to us.
6.cn: 所以你要完成任务要回家，回到她身边，为了我们，你一定要回来。

7.en: Keep it simple, eyes on the ball, shoulders up, see your foot hit it, drive through the ball. Finish at your target!
7.cn: 简单点，看着球，抬起肩膀，看见你的脚踢到球，把球踢飞，完成目标！

8.en: Art class. This is you, Maya. Today, we finish our first paintings, and Mr. Jackson gets to see how talented you are.
8.cn: 美术课，是你表现自己的机会，玛雅，今天我们完成自己的第一幅作品，杰克逊老师会发现你多么有天赋。

9.en: Now to finish the salad, I've got here some dressing. So in here there's some pineapple juice, some lime juice, flavors of the sweet and sour. Lovely.
9.cn: 为了完成沙拉，我要加些沙拉酱，倒一些菠萝汁，一些青柠汁，增加酸甜的味道。很好。

10.en: Here's my question. I successfully negotiated the release of Caroline and Melissa Miller. Then you stepped in. You didn't let me finish the job. Why?
10.cn: 我想问你，我成功的谈判让卡洛琳和梅莉莎·米勒得以释放但你插手进你没让我完成任务，为什么？

11.en: I knew it wouldn't be safe to open the Chamber again while I was still at school, so I decided to leave behind a diary, preserving my 16-year-old self in its pages so that one day, I would be able to lead another to finish Salazar Slytherin's noble work.
11.cn: 在我还待在学校的时候再打开密室实在是太冒险了，所以我决定留下我的日记，把十六岁的我保存在日记里头，直到有一天我能够引导另一个人来完成萨拉札斯莱特林的伟大使命。

15.en: People have got to finish their stories.
15.cn: 说故事的人得把故事说完。

16.en: A sprig or two of coriander. And finish.
16.cn: 加上一两片香菜，大功告成。

17.en: Dad, it's fine, I can finish the dusting.
17.cn: 爸爸，没关系了，我可以做扫灰。

18.en: Just finish that road and get outta here!
18.cn: 快点修完那条路，然后离开这里！

19.en: Well, it's time to finish it. Just a minute.
19.cn: 好吧，那你现在就该写了。再等一下。
